== Overview ==
'''Riconnen's Challenge''' (also referred to as '''Rico's Challenge''' or simply '''Rico''') is a special [[Outlands|outland]] combat arena presented by the '''SatCom Corporation'''. It is a spectator warfare event open to all [[Controller|Controllers]] and consists of two distinct challenge modes: the '''Duel''' and '''Sudden Death'''.

Unlike the open-world patrol zones of [[Vulcore Plain|Vulcore]] and the [[Talsian Warfront|Talsian Warfront]], Riconnen's Challenge is a structured arena event — Controllers enter a series of pre-set combat rounds against named opponents. The rules are simple: '''survive'''.

