{{Quote|The SatCom corporation is proud to present the latest and greatest in spectator warfare — Riconnen's Challenge. Open to all able and willing warriors, the rules are simple. Survive. Stand your ground in the Duel Ring against single opponents or dare to enter Sudden Death — Riconnen's ultimate challenge where you only get one chance to prove your worth. Time your challenges carefully though, for the first to win will reap all the benefits.}}

== The Duel ==

=== Rules ===
* '''One bot only''' — no squad support.
* There is '''no BM restriction'''; any bot may enter regardless of Battle Merit.
* Each Controller can only '''win the Duel once'''.
* Once a player has won the Duel, prize earnings for subsequent winners decrease based on the total number of preceding winners.
* '''5 rounds''' must be completed to win.

=== Prize ===
The '''first Controller''' to win the Duel is awarded:
* '''$1,000,000''' credits
* '''1,000,000''' experience points (also awarded to the bot)

The first recorded Duel champion was '''Sturmovik'''.

