== Sudden Death ==

=== Rules ===
* Entering Sudden Death is allowed '''only once''' — there is no second chance.
* Enemy squads range from '''4 million BM''' up to '''10 million BM'''.
* '''8 rounds''' must be completed to win.
* Be sure you are ready before entering.

=== Prize ===
The '''first Controller''' to survive all 8 rounds of Sudden Death will be awarded a unique '''[[CyCorps Leviathan|CyLeviathan]]'''.

=== Sudden Death Rounds ===

