== General Strategy ==

=== Duel ===
* Only one bot is allowed — choose your best single-combat bot.
* The Duel escalates significantly in difficulty by Round 4 (Kraken's 9000 projected shield) and Round 5 (Storm's dual [[Plasma Anamorph]] shields totalling 12,000 HP).
* '''Round 4 (Kraken)''': Bring heavy shield-stripping weapons. The 9,000 projected shield must be depleted before you can damage the chassis. [[Shield Displacer]], [[Heavy Shield Disruptor]], and [[Syphon MKII]] are recommended.
* '''Round 5 (Storm)''': The [[Storm Bringer]] has only 25% accuracy but deals 3,500 shield damage per hit. Maximise your own shield HP and bring energy-drain weapons to deplete Storm's [[Magmatic Pyroclast]] reactor.

=== Sudden Death ===
* You only get '''one attempt''' — do not enter until fully prepared.
* The BM of enemy squads ranges from ~4M to nearly 15M.
* Recommended preparation:
** Maximum-tech shields (e.g. [[Plasma Anamorph]], [[Argon Web]])
** High-energy reactor (e.g. [[Magmatic Pyroclast]])
** Mix of shield-stripping and armour-damage weapons
** Modules that boost deflection and fire rate
* SD3: Destroy Spotters first or the mortars will devastate your squad.
* SD7: The Annihilator is the priority target.
* SD8: The hardest encounter in the game at 14,937K BM — bring everything you have.

